```plantuml
@startuml hyeonsangjeon_youtube-dl-nas

actor User
participant "Web Interface" as WebInterface
participant "REST API" as RESTAPI
participant "WebSocket Server" as WebSocketServer
participant "Auth Module" as AuthModule
participant "Download Queue" as DownloadQueue
participant "Download Worker" as DownloadWorker
participant "yt-dlp/youtube-dl" as Downloader

User -> WebInterface: Request Login
WebInterface -> AuthModule: Validate Credentials
AuthModule --> WebInterface: Authentication Success

User -> WebInterface: Submit Download Request
alt login required
    WebInterface -> AuthModule: Validate Credentials
    AuthModule --> WebInterface: Authentication Success
end
WebInterface -> RESTAPI: Forward Download Request
RESTAPI -> AuthModule: Validate API Credentials
AuthModule --> RESTAPI: Authentication Success
RESTAPI -> DownloadQueue: Enqueue Download Request

DownloadQueue -> DownloadWorker: Dequeue and Process Request
DownloadWorker -> Downloader: Execute Download Command
Downloader --> DownloadWorker: Download Success/Failure

DownloadWorker -> WebSocketServer: Notify Download Status
WebSocketServer -> WebInterface: Update Download Status
WebInterface -> User: Display Download Status

User -> WebInterface: Request Download Queue Status
WebInterface -> WebSocketServer: Connect WebSocket
WebSocketServer -> DownloadQueue: Fetch Queue Status
DownloadQueue --> WebSocketServer: Return Queue Status
WebSocketServer -> WebInterface: Send Queue Status
WebInterface -> User: Display Queue Status

@enduml
```